General.Name: Immunovia publ AB
General.Description: Immunovia AB (publ), a diagnostic company, develops and commercializes blood-based diagnostics for cancer in Sweden and internationally. It offers IMMray PanCan-d, a blood-based test for the early detection of pancreatic cancer. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
